title: Jimmy Chang from Sect, Undying and Catharsis
itunes:title: Jimmy Chang from Sect, Undying and Catharsis
description:
North Carolina month continues! This week we have Jimmy Chang from Sect, Undying and Catharsis hopping on Skype one afternoon and talking about life in North Carolina, early touring experiences and being bad at business. He's also got one of the best jumps in hardcore, so pay attention! Bridge Nine Records has two great Agnostic Front pre-orders up now, check it out! Use the code PC100WORDS for 10% off of your order at Rockabilia. Incredible merch, reasonable prices and independently owned. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
